window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A major discovery at a geothermal drilling site in Iceland is the beginning of an astonishing story that began 15,000 years ago on earth. A story that has been debated by our holy men for the millennia: Is there life after death, or do we just disappear? Billionaire Baron Bradford wants to know for sure. He wants to find a way to take his vast wealth with him to his next life.&nbsp;</p> <p>If you were a billionaire, would you want to leave it all behind and start over again with nothing?&nbsp; What if you really could take it all with you...but how?</p> <p><i>The Inheritance</i> is a vivid thriller that could change the way you look at life. A powerful mystery full of action, conflict, and astonishing disclosure. A tightly crafted plot by Emmy Award-winning journalist and author Rick Hull. <i>The Inheritance</i> will show you that history as we know it is woefully incomplete!</p>"; 
